checks.name: Code-Review
checks.reason: 1 out of last 4 changesets reviewed before merge -- score normalized to 2

documentation.short: Determines if the project requires code review before pull requests (aka merge requests) are merged.

checks.name: Maintained
checks.reason: 0 commit(s) out of 30 and 0 issue activity out of 30 found in the last 90 days -- score normalized to 0

documentation.short: Determines if the project is "actively maintained".
Determines if the project has an OpenSSF (formerly CII) Best Practices Badge.
